{"tid":126221,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"（少圖更少字）唔係呀嘛 北海道負十五度？","createTime":"2017-02-19T07:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T16:20:44.000Z","uid":77887,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de0db39d171a215adeb2ab583a444c2849095b4b","tid":126221,"uid":77887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T07:46:29.000Z","msg":"一直都好想去北海道 因為從來未見過雪<br />\n所以就想趁雪祭見識下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（去完發現無雪嘅北海道係無特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n呀肥係個窮撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以係先飛東京再轉香草去新千歲<br />\n<br />\n行程是這樣 <br />\nDay 1 2 東京<br />\nDay 3 - 9 札幌小樽函館登別<br />\nDay 10 東京<br />\n<br />\n其實咁排係濕鳩 不過雪祭啲酒店真係好鬼full<br />\n十二月尾已經得返勁貴個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲買機票真係慘過食屎<br />\n唯有就平酒店同埋airbnb嘅時間啦<br />\n（但去到札幌係比想像中少人的<br />\n極度懷疑啲人乜屎都book曬先 <br />\n去到前一個星期先撻訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"38060c011e6bde378644cbe96710a6a87ab1361f","tid":126221,"uid":77887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T07:55:33.000Z","msg":"東京就唔講咁多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一日去到成田都夜晚<br />\n即刻仆返屋企準備第二朝陪娘親去迪士尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B9Gd768.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB9Gd768.jpg&h=505fb357&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n發現日本人真係好有氣氛 戴曬costume<br />\n連啲架仔都戴啲公仔帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  （無圖）<br />\n但最sad嘅係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個晚兩次煙花都係let it go個兩隻騎呢女人做主題"},{"pid":"b275508dcad5279d8758d1de8f1b3065b57a4814","tid":126221,"uid":77887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T08:05:02.000Z","msg":"Day 3<br />\n晨早流流出發去機場 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K954063.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK954063.jpg&h=f1708977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/160125_72287197e5991f264aa33ee5ba56e9aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F19%2F160125_72287197e5991f264aa33ee5ba56e9aa.jpg&h=ac130699&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐9點15機去札幌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/160304_3ded6b1bf6f4c9f7944f261c4bcef3b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F19%2F160304_3ded6b1bf6f4c9f7944f261c4bcef3b4.jpg&h=6b4b6637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知咩山 特別高咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O2jG44a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO2jG44a.jpg&h=16243407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一望落去全部都係白色<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/160305_2534e026f42ad2ac42ced6d4865d26e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F19%2F160305_2534e026f42ad2ac42ced6d4865d26e3.jpg&h=751ad020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n超級感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5074fda7de929e4cd253cf1ef5bf4c2af8c3a58","tid":126221,"uid":12297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T08:30:23.000Z","msg":"岩岩去完道東+札幌雪祭<br />\n好彩天氣唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋冇想像中咁凍<br />\n最凍果時係屈斜路湖睇日出先負13度左右"},{"pid":"b6f2bd6eff8d3b9e8cfd02d4aec8d09778072248","tid":126221,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T08:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6128e154de97dc4ed6c3363fcda8ef8431ac5549","tid":126221,"uid":77887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T10:12:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩去完道東+札幌雪祭<br />\n好彩天氣唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋冇想像中咁凍<br />\n最凍果時係屈斜路湖睇日出先負13度左右</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n道東好似好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔夠時間去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1900e5bccae9fb9a87b160456ed1f251a6561c","tid":126221,"uid":77887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T10:12:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今晚再出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d4bd0836bd1f3e5b651d999a28b18d49f29fc4","tid":126221,"uid":34692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T10:29:01.000Z","msg":"北海道天氣凍有咩出奇<br />\n定係你覺得太熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1470fa2dbcea6c7bef4aaa533cae997868615b3b","tid":126221,"uid":77887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:08:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>北海道天氣凍有咩出奇<br />\n定係你覺得太熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇埋先啦巴打 等陣會講到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4bdfeff18a3880a77975123b5aed92b148948c","tid":126221,"uid":36473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:12:15.000Z","msg":"係富士山"},{"pid":"b1014e1f67b0e19177b9f3d49f1081404f7cabb6","tid":126221,"uid":31629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:17:12.000Z","msg":"你個標題好想負評<br />\n令我諗起D又要睇雪又要凍去到又屌依樣個樣D人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後冇負評"},{"pid":"18fbe772d0af1064ce907328177444dc40dbd37f","tid":126221,"uid":649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:19:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個標題好想負評<br />\n令我諗起D又要睇雪又要凍去到又屌依樣個樣D人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後冇負評</blockquote><br />\n唔知點解睇完topic 都想負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a364a59076bb05e7b1b86ae80b2d3107d007b6","tid":126221,"uid":38351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:23:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你個標題好想負評<br />\n令我諗起D又要睇雪又要凍去到又屌依樣個樣D人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後冇負評</blockquote><br />\n唔知點解睇完topic 都想負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger <br />\n睇fb 見到啲人去東北，北海道負2度已經叫晒救命咁。痴痴哋，去得預咗凍架啦！未到負10 度好心咪出聲叫凍。負2度叫暖啦！"},{"pid":"e8ff7c1a96c98d82be6ad07ae473eccd9f58a2a4","tid":126221,"uid":49260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:23:18.000Z","msg":"最憎雪 凍撚到仆街"},{"pid":"dce5f488c855978016128621fc2ed50b9b9f0f6a","tid":126221,"uid":69698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:24:12.000Z","msg":"前日先落機，北海道冇想象中禁凍"},{"pid":"83e9aa3918fb8602d981b041e066aafc23fb674e","tid":126221,"uid":49260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:24:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你個標題好想負評<br />\n令我諗起D又要睇雪又要凍去到又屌依樣個樣D人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後冇負評</blockquote><br />\n唔知點解睇完topic 都想負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger <br />\n睇fb 見到啲人去東北，北海道負2度已經叫晒救命咁。痴痴哋，去得預咗凍架啦！未到負10 度好心咪出聲叫凍。負2度叫暖啦！</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5895145ee4378f782831b94a5b5e5395facabe76","tid":126221,"uid":77887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:33:35.000Z","msg":"各位唔好屌住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n接落黎要分享件極戇鳩嘅事<br />\n解釋埋點解個名咁戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說出發前一日 屋企人send左張咁嘅圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/192319_2b37bf65449c978f250d4a8b66e303fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F19%2F192319_2b37bf65449c978f250d4a8b66e303fc.jpg&h=cc74d2ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到負廿度 心諗今次仆街喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係話負幾咋咩<br />\n平時係香港十度都鳩縮唔想出門<br />\n到底低多三十度會點 又興奮又淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果帶左兩件羽絨去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知 機都未落 <br />\n靚女空姐宣佈landing嘅時候發現<br />\n屌 札榥係負幾度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來一路cap嘅係成個北海道平均嘅天氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就是這樣 未出發先戇鳩左一轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0cefc7afb7fabad6e55459a12c946c57b9f3bd","tid":126221,"uid":77887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:34:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係富士山</blockquote><br />\n張圖係就到新千歲landing嘅時候影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係富士咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ee251a4f99818cd1d4d50660846f6317d969f6","tid":126221,"uid":77887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:35:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最憎雪 凍撚到仆街</blockquote><br />\n落雪唔涷 融融地個下真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5312c331182ad55df00c35ce7f5dd3c41a77fc8","tid":126221,"uid":77887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:37:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前日先落機，北海道冇想象中禁凍</blockquote><br />\n有太陽嘅時候 <br />\n一件heat tech 加fleece 著多件風褸已經夠頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可惜一到夜晚就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a12505c8e734cefa0817a269970f4b54ed916b8","tid":126221,"uid":31629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:46:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係富士山</blockquote><br />\n張圖係就到新千歲landing嘅時候影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係富士咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n羊蹄山黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ffdbe1cddcb768f4d786511c7290ef813b6628a","tid":126221,"uid":45558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2120h60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2120h60.jpg&h=0f474d4d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/03Q63bh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F03Q63bh.jpg&h=d185cda6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/66ayt86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F66ayt86.jpg&h=be47d8eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岩岩番黎，真係唔算好凍，因為知道凍會做好準備，反應覺得香港凍啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e02f176155d264f097e850797d786bf5819a6e5","tid":126221,"uid":77887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T12:18:40.000Z","msg":"Day 4 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rS0008e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrS0008e.jpg&h=b3adabba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n坐4分鐘天狗山纜車<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/201149_df3de3fcc59222cdbc170b1f21b0bc3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F19%2F201149_df3de3fcc59222cdbc170b1f21b0bc3d.jpg&h=1d580a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小樽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 5 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/38SF0dZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F38SF0dZ.jpg&h=07f10d3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n堺町 估唔到幾多嘢食<br />\n<br />\n其實個人覺得小樽係overrated <br />\n絕對可以即日來回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雪燈之路係靚嘅 但成個小樽最靚就係得呢個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n餐廳好多都早收 <br />\n不過壽司同三角市場ok抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da841f2f965690dea133e212f36fbfb2df6225b7","tid":126221,"uid":38351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T12:25:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各位唔好屌住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n接落黎要分享件極戇鳩嘅事<br />\n解釋埋點解個名咁戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說出發前一日 屋企人send左張咁嘅圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/192319_2b37bf65449c978f250d4a8b66e303fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F19%2F192319_2b37bf65449c978f250d4a8b66e303fc.jpg&h=cc74d2ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到負廿度 心諗今次仆街喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係話負幾咋咩<br />\n平時係香港十度都鳩縮唔想出門<br />\n到底低多三十度會點 又興奮又淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果帶左兩件羽絨去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知 機都未落 <br />\n靚女空姐宣佈landing嘅時候發現<br />\n屌 札榥係負幾度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來一路cap嘅係成個北海道平均嘅天氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就是這樣 未出發先戇鳩左一轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n哈哈，樓主被騙喇！<br />\n帶廣道東係凍，早排零下30添。<br />\n道央道南暖好多，除非大風衣物又唔擋風，咁就真係凍到硬晒汰"},{"pid":"1102549c853dc847f96fbcb46324815b753cb675","tid":126221,"uid":77887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:02:57.000Z","msg":"Day 6<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/205832_921b90273988b94953ada306fc3f9492.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F19%2F205832_921b90273988b94953ada306fc3f9492.jpg&h=015b08d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南千歲 <br />\n<br />\n因為痾屎miss左班車去支笏湖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就咁鳩左一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 7<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zF28uJ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzF28uJ3.jpg&h=4aab0269&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n登別地獄谷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XsRw278.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXsRw278.jpg&h=31f5450c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P6eBH8Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP6eBH8Z.jpg&h=379e3c11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n順手搭落函館<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Y5720F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Y5720F.jpg&h=49c504d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一出jr站 撞正有煙花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}